# Indexer cache — written by the LSP/IDE server into each project's
# .vscode/. Never check it in (committed copies invalidate when
# INDEX_VERSION bumps and confuse fixture-based tests). v11+ adds a
# per-project hash suffix so multiple projects sharing one .vscode/
# don't trample each other; the un-suffixed names are kept here for
# users upgrading from pre-v29 caches.
.vscode/callchain-index-*.msgpack
.vscode/callchain-index.msgpack
.vscode/callchain-index.json
test/fixtures/**/.vscode/
